    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103830/extras/ec403785d2e8ade6cc9d91ad9f401177.avif?t=1739507974\" width=600 height=240 /></span><br><br>您的鸭子们经过不懈努力，积累了大量黄金和钻石，但他们辛辛苦苦赚来的财富却引起了冷酷无情的鸡帮的注意。这些长满羽毛的恶魔的任务就是掠夺您的财富，消灭您的鸭子大军。<br><br>Quacker Bros》具有令人上瘾的游戏性、无尽的挑战性和羽毛的趣味性，可为战略爱好者和休闲玩家提供数小时的娱乐。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103830/extras/50b8e962d164df8f1bb03bab2219521f.poster.avif?t=1739507974\" width=600 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103830/extras/50b8e962d164df8f1bb03bab2219521f.webm?t=1739507974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103830/extras/50b8e962d164df8f1bb03bab2219521f.mp4?t=1739507974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >是时候嘎嘎反击了！升级你的鸭子，解锁新的强大单位，加固你的防御，抵御日益凶猛的鸡群进攻。</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103830/extras/48aa2dfbbdfd9d9e0d5f4a52f9e4c3d0.poster.avif?t=1739507974\" width=600 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103830/extras/48aa2dfbbdfd9d9e0d5f4a52f9e4c3d0.webm?t=1739507974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103830/extras/48aa2dfbbdfd9d9e0d5f4a52f9e4c3d0.mp4?t=1739507974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>组建并指挥一支不可阻挡的鸭子部队，每只鸭子都有独特的能力。战略性地部署您的部队，保护您的丰收免受一波又一波鸡肉入侵者的攻击。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103830/extras/99841919eefb32cde20b148479f6d6b9.poster.avif?t=1739507974\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103830/extras/99841919eefb32cde20b148479f6d6b9.webm?t=1739507974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103830/extras/99841919eefb32cde20b148479f6d6b9.mp4?t=1739507974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>但是要小心！鸡是狡猾而无情的。它们会孵化出新的战术和更强大的小鸟来挑战您的防御。您能智取这些长满羽毛的敌人，确保您的财富吗？只有最有策略、最无畏的鸭子指挥官才能获胜。",
